---

<section class="about section" id="about">
	<div class="container">
		<div class="section-heading">
			<h2>About Me</h2>
			<span class="underline"></span>
		</div>

		<div class="about-grid">
			<div class="about-text">
				<p>
					I'm Szilard Tatar, a video editor specializing in lyric videos and music
					videos for independent artists, labels, and creators around the world.
				</p>
				<p>
					With a passion for visual storytelling and rhythm, I help musicians bring
					their songs to life through clean typography, dynamic motion, and
					cinematic edits that connect with fans on every platform.
				</p>
				<p>
					Whether you need a lyric video for your next single, a full music video
					edit, or social-ready vertical cuts — I work closely with you from
					concept to final delivery.
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="about-photo">
				<img
					src="/images/profile.jpg.jpg"
					alt="Szilard Tatar"
					width="320"
					height="320"
					loading="lazy"
				/>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.section {
		padding: var(--section-pad);
	}

	.about-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 280px;
		gap: 3rem;
		align-items: center;
	}

	.about-text p {
		color: var(--color-muted);
		margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
	}

	.about-photo img {
		width: 280px;
		height: 280px;
		border-radius: 50%;
		object-fit: cover;
		margin: 0 auto;
		box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(196, 92, 255, 0.15);
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.about-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			text-align: center;
		}

		.about-photo {
			order: -1;
		}
	}
</style>
